# CS8.401 POIS - Programming Assignments

Interactive implementation of the Minicrypt reduction chain with a Python backend and a React webapp.

This repository currently has working implementations for:
- PA00 (Reduction Explorer scaffold)
- PA01 (OWF and PRG)
- PA02 (PRF via GGM)
- PA03 (CPA-secure symmetric encryption)
- PA04 (Modes of operation: CBC, OFB, CTR)
- PA05 (MACs: PRF-MAC, CBC-MAC, EUF-CMA game, length-extension demo)
- PA06 (CCA-secure Encrypt-then-MAC)
- PA07 (Merkle-Damgard transform)

---

