| PA02 | Implemented |
| PA03 | Implemented |
| PA04 | Implemented |
| PA05 | Implemented |
| PA06 | Implemented |
| PA07 | Implemented |
| PA08-PA20 | Stubs / pending |

Note: PA05 includes an HMAC forward stub intentionally deferred to PA10.

---

## Project Layout

```
src/pois/
  assignments/
    pa00.py ... pa20.py   # Assignment modules
  registry.py             # Assignment route map
  runner.py               # run_assignment("PAxx") loader
  cli.py                  # Team workflow CLI
  workflow.py             # Claim/complete/status state handling

webapp/
  src/
    App.tsx               # Tab container (PA00-PA07 panels)
    Pa01Panel.tsx ... Pa07Panel.tsx
    foundations.ts, routing.ts
    prg.ts, ggm.ts, enc.ts, modes.ts, mac.ts, cca.ts, merkle.ts
```

---

## Prerequisites

- Python 3.10+
- Node.js 18+ and npm

---

## Setup (macOS / Linux)

```bash
cd POIS-Programming-Assignments

python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e .

cd webapp
npm install
```

## Setup (Windows PowerShell)

```powershell
cd POIS-Programming-Assignments

python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -e .

cd webapp
npm install
```

---

## Run Backend Demos

From repository root:

```bash
source .venv/bin/activate

python -c "from pois.assignments.pa04 import PA04; print(PA04().run_demo())"
python -c "from pois.assignments.pa05 import PA05; print(PA05().run_demo())"
python -c "from pois.assignments.pa06 import PA06; print(PA06().run_demo())"
python -c "from pois.assignments.pa07 import PA07; print(PA07().run_demo())"
```

Or through the assignment runner:

```bash
python -c "from pois.runner import run_assignment; print(run_assignment('PA07'))"
```

---

## Run Webapp

```bash
cd webapp
npm run dev
```

Open: http://localhost:5173

Production build:

```bash
npm run build
npm run preview
```

---

## Workflow CLI (Team Task Tracking)

From repository root:

```bash
python -m pois.cli init
python -m pois.cli status
python -m pois.cli next --member Kushal
python -m pois.cli complete --member Kushal --task PA07
```

Workflow files:
- workflow/tasks.json (task dependencies and ownership)
- workflow/state.json (claimed/completed/history)

---

## Quick Pre-Push Checklist

From repository root:

```bash
source .venv/bin/activate
python -m compileall -q src

python - <<'PY'
from pois.runner import run_assignment
for tid in ['PA04','PA05','PA06','PA07']:
    out = run_assignment(tid)
    print(tid, 'OK', len(out))
PY

cd webapp
npm run build
```

If all commands pass, the repo is in good shape to push.

---

## Notes

- This is an educational implementation with toy parameters in several places.
- cryptography is used for the AES-based PRF plug-in where required.
- Unimplemented assignments intentionally raise NotImplementedError.
